7\n| ''[[Hard Sun]]''\n| Charlie Hicks\n|\n|-\n| 2020\u2013present \n| ''[[Home Before Dark (TV series)|Home Before Dark]]''\n| Matthew Lisko\n|\n|}\n\n==Discography==\n===Soundtracks===\n{| class=wikitable\n|-\n! Year\n! Song\n! Credits / Notes\n! Film/Soundtrack\n|-\n| rowspan=\"11\"|2007\n| \"[[Girl (Beatles song)|Girl]]\"\n|\n| rowspan=\"11\"| ''[[Across the Universe (film)#Soundtrack|Across the Universe]]''\n|-\n| \"[[All My Loving]]\"\n|\n|-\n| \"[[With A Little Help From My Friends]]\"\n|<small>(with [[Joe Anderson (actor)|Joe Anderson]])</small>\n|-\n|\"[[I've Just Seen A Face]]\"\n|\n|-\n|\"[[Dear Prudence]]\"\n|<small>(with [[Joe Anderson (actor)|Joe Anderson]], [[Dana Fuchs]] & <br>[[Evan Rachel Wood]])</small>\n|-\n|\"[[Because (The Beatles song)|Because]]\"\n|<small>(with [[Joe Anderson (actor)|Joe Anderson]], [[T. V. Carpio]], <br>[[Dana Fuchs]], [[Martin Luther McCoy]] <br>& [[Evan Rachel Wood]])</small>\n|-\n|\"[[Something (Beatles song)|Something]]\"\n|\n|-\n|\"[[Strawberry Fields Forever]]\"\n|<small>(with [[Joe Anderson (actor)|Joe Anderson]])</small>\n|-\n|\"[[Revolution (Beatles song)|Revolution]]\"\n|\n|-\n|\"[[Across the Universe]]\"\n|\n|-\n|\"[[All You Need Is Love]]\"\n|<small>(with [[T. V. Carpio]], [[Dana Fuchs]] <br>& [[Martin Luther McCoy]])</small>\n|-\n||2008\n| \"Lost Everything\"{{ref|note1}}\n|\n|| ''[[21 (2008 film)|21]]''\n|-\n| rowspan=\"6\"|2009\n| \"Mistake The Enemy\"\n|<small>(Writer and performer)</small><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0924129/soundtrack|title=Crossing Over (2009)|publisher=IMDb.com|accessdate=6 April 2013}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"3\"| ''[[Crossing Over (film)|Crossing Over]]''\n|-\n| \"Make Your Mind Up\"\n|<small>(Writer and performer)</small>\n|-\n| \"[[Hine ma tov]]\"\n|<small>(Traditional)</small>\n|-\n| \"Heartless\"\n|\n| rowspan=\"3\"| ''[[Heartless (2009 film)|Heartless]]''\n|-\n| \"The Other Me\"\n|\n|-\n| \"Panic and Magic\"\n|<small>(O'Brien/Stoney/Sturgess)</small><ref>{{cite web|u